Bug ID: BUG_300
Title: Cart items are displayed in an inconsistent order after page refresh
Module: Shopping Cart
Steps to Reproduce:
1.	Open website.
2.	Add three or more products to the cart in a specific order.
3.	Open the Cart page.
4.	Note the order of the products.
5.	Refresh the page multiple times.
6.	Observe the order after each refresh.
Expected Result:
The cart should display items in a consistent order after every refresh, such as:
•	the order in which they were added, or
•	another defined sorting order that remains consistent.
Actual Result:
The order of products changes after refreshing the Cart page, making the sequence inconsistent.
Severity: Medium
Priority: Medium

Bug ID:BUG_301
Title: Selected category is not visually highlighted after clicking "Phones"
Module: Product Categories
Steps to Reproduce:
1.	Open the website homepage.
2.	Click on the Phones category.
3.	Observe the category list.
Expected Result:
The selected category should be visually highlighted (e.g., different color, background, or active state) to indicate it is currently selected.
Actual Result:
The selected category is not highlighted, making it difficult for users to identify the active category.
Severity & Priority
•	Severity: Low (the functionality still works—the products are filtered correctly).
•	Priority: Low (it doesn't block any user action, but it affects usability).

